	"Initialize this light"

	attenuation _ B3DLightAttenuation constant: 1.0 linear: 0.0 squared: 0.0.! !!WonderlandPositionalLight methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'jsp 4/29/1999 11:10'!initializeFor: aWonderland
